  - critical-thinking
---

Information provided by an LLM can often sound very credible and still be very wrong, so I have become automatically distrustful until I have made my own sense of what AI provides.

This scepticism has naturally extended beyond AI to include what I read and the interactions I have with others. AI trained me to interrogate everything, and that habit stuck.

The irony: AI's unreliability made me a more critical thinker in general.
